name: Euglossa D'ecorata
description:
Augmented Reality Digital Sculpture of Glitched Insect by Micah Alhadeff; Wrapped in Analog Video Feedback Textures by CIPOTE. 

"Insecta Teknika" are hybrid-insects, fused together by combining two different modes of electronic media (3D Modeling + Analog Video Feedback), in order to create one glitched cyber-exoskeleton. Welcome to the electronic-insectarium - a metamorphosis of nature into technology.

"Euglossa D'ecorata" is the 2nd release of "Insecta Teknika" - a Micah Alhadeff x CIPOTE collaboration.
